2 total enrollment and enrollment by grade;
3 (c) The schools, grades, and programs the district will offer;
4 (d) The facilities that the district will maintain to house those schools, grades,
5 and programs that includes a facilities plan for the first fully operational
6 year;
7 (e) The transportation services the district will provide to students that includes
8 a transportation plan for the first fully operational year;
9 (f) The food services the district will provide to students that includes a food
10 services plan for the first fully operational year;
11 (g) The process the district will follow in conforming to the Individuals with
