21 operational school year;
22 (k) A district technology plan that provides for the technological needs of the
23 district and schools throughout the transition and the first fully operational
24 school year;
25 (l) Transition services for high school students to ensure that students remain
26 on track to graduate during the transition and the first fully operational
27 school year; and
